title: 17 Things Girls Actually Mean When They Say "I'm Fine"
text:

livingjoke.tumblr.com ID: 10704579 3. She’s contemplating the evolutionary process. what she says: i'm fine what she means: do racoons have human hands or do humans have racoon hands
— yams!!! (@sunshinecanine) ID: 10704606 4. She’s emotional about the well deserved success of Hamilton . View this image › 
the-other-fifty-one.tumblr.com ID: 10704586 5. She’s worried about child safety and the biased hiring process in High School Musical . View this image › 
breathe-narry.tumblr.com ID: 10704600 6. She’s questioning the extent of the personification in Cars . What she says: I'm fine What she means: does Lightning McQueen have car insurance or life insurance????
— taylor (@freetobe_T) ID: 10704608 7. Or she’s picking apart the illogical plot holes in Hannah Montana: The Movie . View this image › 
letminghaosing.tumblr.com ID: 10704621 8. She still feels like Tyra Banks is personally targeting her. View this image › 
charmingdeadpool.tumblr.com ID: 10704695 9. She’s romanticising Gone Girl ing herself. what she says: im fine what she means: I'm so much happier now that I'm dead. Technically missing. Soon to be presumed dead. Gone. And my la
— em c hammer (@patrohcls) ID: 10704770 10. She’s thinking of the traumatic consequences of the custody arrangement in The Parent Trap . View this image › 
mattymurrdick.tumblr.com ID: 10704715 11. And she was deeply moved by The Bee Movie . What she says: I'm fine What she means: According to all known laws of aviation, there is no way a bee should be able to fly
— quinnie (@tmcripple) ID: 10704673 12. She thinks Steve Buscemi is a stellar guy who deserves nothing but love and respect. View this image › 
stevebuscemi4prez.tumblr.com ID: 10704725 13. She wants to understand the relative sizes of the characters in Spongebob Squarepants . View this image › 
dad1.tumblr.com ID: 10704728 14. Or she’s dwelling over the inner workings of the Hogwarts postal system. View this image › 
damnmalec.tumblr.com ID: 10704730 15. She’s angry about how Legally Blonde undersold Elle Woods’ intellect. View this image › 
standbyyourmantis.tumblr.com ID: 10704734 16. She wants justice for Robb Stark’s undeserved death. what she says: i'm fine what she means: i will never have closure until robb stark is laid to rest in the crypts of winterfell
— emily (@jaredspadaIecki) ID: 10704764 17. And she just really fucking hates The Minions . View this image ›
